    "title": "Mid-Level Plant Manager at Dalmia Bharat",
    "description": "We at Dalmia Bharat are looking for an experienced Plant Manager based out of Meerut. If you are a result-oriented professional with a passion for excellence, we want to hear from you.\n\nAbout Dalmia Bharat:\nDalmia Bharat is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Prepare production cost analysis and efficiency reports\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n• Train and supervise shop floor workers and supervisors\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Com / M.Com / MBA Finance\n• 10-15 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in Six Sigma\n• Proficiency in Root Cause Analysis\n• Proficiency in Supply Chain Management\n• Proficiency in PLC/SCADA\n• Proficiency in Statistical Process Control\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in ERP Systems\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Professional development and training programs\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Flexible working hours\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 20 LPA - 40 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Meerut, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Dalmia Bharat!",
